  "text": "A conventional distortion metric for the source coding of the matrix S is \u03b4S 2 . However, this may be very different from the squared error distortion in the matrix-vector product result which is given by \u03b4x 2 . Therefore, we would like to relate the distortion metric for S to the quantity \u03b4x [CITATION_1] .",
